          <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-800">Inder Sahani</h4>
            <span
              class="text-xs bg-pink-100 text-pink-800 px-2 py-1 rounded-full"
              >Day 3</span
            >
          </div>

          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2 text-sm">
            Multi-talented artist known for his soulful Punjabi vocals and
            charismatic stage presence. A true cultural icon who has bridged
            regional and mainstream music.
          </p>

          <div class="flex items-center mt-4">
            <a
